preliminary notes

types of questions
  pick 1 of 4
  true / false
  pick a few from a list (all of the above / only b and c / etc)

information in question
  word (dictionary)
  thing that would have a wikipedia article 
    define 
    where did this originate
    where is this most popular
    when did this originate
  science:
    how much of any number
  event:
    when did this happen
    where
    who was involved
  language:
    what's the word for this in this foreign language
  geography
    population
    capitol
    neighboring states
    neighboring oceans

categories that i wouldn't think of, but people will like:
  food/drink
  plays
  classical music